sp;불안&nbsp;등<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">-&nbsp;체력과&nbsp;면역력,&nbsp;기억력&nbsp;저하<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\" color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">-&nbsp;갱년기&nbsp;및&nbsp;폐경기&nbsp;증후군<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><br></span><span style=\" color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span><span style=\" color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">-&nbsp;수험생과&nbsp;스트레스가&nbsp;많은&nbsp;현대인의&nbsp;정신을&nbsp;맑게</span></span></span><br></span></span><span><br></span> <br> <br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">공진단과&nbsp;경옥고는&nbsp;남녀노소&nbsp;온&nbsp;가족이&nbsp;드실수있으니, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">이수한의원의&nbsp;공진단과&nbsp;경옥고로&nbsp;우리&nbsp;가족&nbsp;건강&nbsp;챙겨보아요 </span><br><span> <br></span><span><br></span><span><br></span><span><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b><b>추석맞이 건강선물 이벤트로 한정수량 할인중이니&nbsp;</b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b>서두르세요</b></span></b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\"><br></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>이벤트 기간은</b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b> </b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 47, 34);\" class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b>9월 13일 </b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b>~</b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 47, 34);\" class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b> 10월 7일</b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se_fs_T2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>까지 합니다</b></span><br><br> <br> <br> <br> <br> <br> <br> <!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<!-- SE_DOC_CONTENTS_END -->\n<div class=\"__se_doc_title_end\" id=\"se_doc_contents_end\"></div>\n<div id=\"SEDOC-1505204423782--2138907071_se_doc_footer\" class=\"